originalSql:
SELECT 
    CONCAT(s.s_name, ' from ', r.r_name) AS supplier_info,
    COUNT(DISTINCT o.o_orderkey) AS total_orders,
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue,
    AVG(p.p_retailprice) AS avg_part_price,
    STRING_AGG(DISTINCT p.p_name, ', ') AS part_names
FROM 
    supplier s
JOIN 
    nation n ON s.s_nationkey = n.n_nationkey
JOIN 
    region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey
JOIN 
    partsupp ps ON s.s_suppkey = ps.ps_suppkey
JOIN 
    part p ON ps.ps_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    lineitem l ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey
JOIN 
    orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey
WHERE 
    r.r_name LIKE 'Europe%' AND 
    l.l_shipdate BETWEEN '1997-01-01' AND '1997-12-31' 
GROUP BY 
    s.s_name, r.r_name
HAVING 
    SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) > 100000
ORDER BY 
    total_revenue DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t5"."SUPPLIER_INFO", "t5"."SUPPLIER_INFO") AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", "t5"."TOTAL_ORDERS", "t5"."TOTAL_REVENUE", "t5"."AVG_PART_PRICE", "t5"."PART_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT "supplier"."s_name", "t1"."r_name", MIN(CONCAT("supplier"."s_name", ' from ', "t1"."r_name")) AS "SUPPLIER_INFO", COUNT(DISTINCT "orders"."o_orderkey") AS "TOTAL_ORDERS", SUM("t0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t0"."l_discount")) AS "TOTAL_REVENUE", AVG("part"."p_retailprice") AS "AVG_PART_PRICE", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "part"."p_name", ', ') AS "PART_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT *
FROM "lineitem"
WHERE "l_shipdate" >= DATE '1997-01-01' AND "l_shipdate" <= DATE '1997-12-31') AS "t0"
INNER JOIN "orders" ON "t0"."l_orderkey" = "orders"."o_orderkey"
INNER JOIN ((SELECT *
FROM "s1"
WHERE "r_name" LIKE 'Europe%') AS "t1" INNER JOIN "nation" ON "t1"."r_regionkey" = "nation"."n_regionkey" INNER JOIN "supplier" ON "nation"."n_nationkey" = "supplier"."s_nationkey" INNER JOIN ("part" INNER JOIN "partsupp" ON "part"."p_partkey" = "partsupp"."ps_partkey") ON "supplier"."s_suppkey" = "partsupp"."ps_suppkey") ON "t0"."l_partkey" = "part"."p_partkey"
GROUP BY "supplier"."s_name", "t1"."r_name"
HAVING SUM("t0"."l_extendedprice" * (1 - "t0"."l_discount")) > 100000.0000
ORDER BY 5 DESC NULLS FIRST) AS "t5"
